title: BlackIsBetter - Jenna J Foxx (SheSquats) NEW 10 May 2018
description: Jenna is a fitspo queen who knows her worth and loves her body. After putting in months of hard work with her trainer Danny, it’s no surprise that she’s developed a crush on him. Today, she wants a different kind of workout and plans to risk it all to indulge in a little sweet treat. Lucky for Jenna, Danny is a skilled trainer who pushes his clients hard and himself even harder. When his favorite client makes a pass at him, he’s more than happy to give her the strong, deep reps she wants. http://imgdone.com/image/Xj2VU http://imgdone.com/image/XjBg1
